                        <interp inst="t18500610-name-954" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN BEARD</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a gas lighter—this tap is mine—I saw it safe in the water-butt in my yard on the night before, about nine o'clock, and missed it about four next morning.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I bought the three taps of a man in the Blackfriars-road.</p>
